fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.models.vars.histories

Class Piece

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.models.vars.histories.Piece

  • public class Piece
extends java.lang.Object
    The class Piece implements a piece in a piecewise-defined function; a piece is defined over an interval and is interpolated by a polynomial.

    Description

    a piece is defined over an interval and is interpolated by a polynomial.

    Glass-box Invariants

     invariant       interval != null && polynomial != null
 invariant       polynomial.value(interval.getBegin()) == interval.getBeginValue()
 invariant       polynomial.value(interval.getEnd()) == interval.getEndValue()

    Black-box Invariants

     invariant       true        // no more invariant

    Created on : 2021-12-09

    Author:
    Jacques Malenfant
